United States: repetition is the mother of wisdom
It is almost comical, with which Schülerstrebsamkeit Barack Obama, the President with his reputation of the brightest, the strategy of his predecessor in the issue of Afghanistan, which he considered himself for the Dümmsten.
When he finally his eagerly-awaited ausschwitzte Afghanistan doctrine, it turned out that he abschrieb this on the Kopierpapier from the Bush-Iraq Szenariovor three years ago.
Not only that, several times in the text itself, the phrase "as in Iraq", he has even used the name of the Bush statement of January 2007 as the name of his own declaration: "new way forward", used without hesitation.
He has even three years of the Bush idea - fresh troop contingents in the troubled by the civil war in Iraq - as "irresponsible and send in their conclusions karastrophische decision".
Subsequent months showed, however, that the recommendations of the military outgoing lands in the only way, and was very successful that it is now in the news about Iraq no longer.
Bush's reputation has not improved by objectively, because he has hintergelassen his successor a much dankbarere starting situation, as it was to be expected.
In Afghanistan, Barack Obama hopes that the miracle repeatedly.
In order to increase the contingent have again asked the military, especially the Oberkommandeur the Afghanistan operation, General Stanley McCristal, even despite the Subordinationsgewohnheiten the vacillating - gunman harshly criticized in the White House.
He called for 40,000 soldiers in order to reverse the situation for the better.
The President has three months, but with no better idea and he has the General wenistens cheated about 10,000 soldiers.
In Europe, he has Pressed the promise of another 5,000, even if he originally at least 10,000 expected.
Highly problematic about the whole Obama strategy is its plan to withdraw troops from Afghanistan in 18 months, and this process to be completed within three years. The whole Obama doctrine leaves more questions than answers.
Some doubt that the cut increase in the same effect as the measure in Iraq.
Also, despite the fratricidal war in recent years, the Iraqi society is relatively well structured, its leaders pay tribute to the values.
The Afghan situation is characterised by the cons indication - you can rely on second and there are no agreements.
Under these conditions, it is difficult to prepare the Afghan security forces, which are used every day to change their minds.
The political institutions, even if they were founded formally correct, that leaves only bogus construction, behind which the patriarchal Stammbeziehungen will make further out.
The balance of interests between the various ethnic groups is unusually complicated, particularly because of the confusion of the conditions that the Pakistan and Iran influences even more complex.
The building of a "strong state", which is the minimalist objective of the whole operation is very unrealistic.
Time horizon of the Obama strategy surprised by his voluntarism
Over the last eight years, the situation in Afghanistan only worse and now it is on the brink of explosion.
To believe that the small soldiers in the war cries about the "early return" from ruptured a miracle, can only create a truly romantic soul, not influenced by facts.
From the political point of view is the date for the withdrawal of troops sheer irresponsibility, because the Taliban as the indirect confession of American defeat.
The last NATO summit showed that the willingness of the Europeans to participate in the combat in Afghanistan, is running out.
Europe's politicians can and want their voters does not explain in what way the security of Germany or Italy , with the war in Iraq .
Another possible factor that can influence the situation radically, is the development of events in Iran.
If the situation continues to deteriorate and the increased sanctions on the Iranians do not work for the United States is a very serious question of whether the problem to be solved not with troops.
This question must be answered in the period in which America after Obama is the winner withdrawal from Afghanistan.
Any solution will also mean a dramatic turn of the Afghan situation.
The only consolation plaster for Barack Obama is the fact that three years until the presidential election and, therefore, there is still enough time so that he can resort to a different strategy, fallls would prove this as a total loss.
