They also asked about, psychological and financial advice for the available, which have more than one child.
The response was not encouraging, said family planning representatives.
Disappointing response
Although officials from a rural town in the external sector of Shanghai said that a recovery in the applications of couples to recognize is that after the launch of the campaign to a second child, the urban districts reported against any change.
In the Huinan municipality with a population of 115 000 than example still per month, only four or five requests.
Disappointed Shanghai officials say that the 2010 expected number of births in the city despite the campaign are still around 165.000 -- slightly higher than 2009, but lower than 2008.
