75% of working mothers have because of their maternity problems in the work
The discrimination in the work has increased in recent years, especially among the younger women who wish to have children.
This result is the CSIC in collaboration with the Institute for Women study "fertility and career women in Spain."
The survey of 9.737 women between 15 and 75 years leaves no doubt about it: 75% of working women see their career are in the labour market because of their motherhood.
The study is laying that there is very broad differences in the decision to start a family and the number of children, depending on whether the women work or not and if so, what kind of work they perform.
Those of you who auβerhalb of the House do no other work only part-time work or a fixed contract, is more likely to be mothers and have more children.
In contrast to postpone the women with a solid job, particularly in the public sector, the creation of a family and motherhood and therefore have fewer children.
"the women in the age group between 35 and 49 years with a solid job get their first child on average only 3.7 years after the drawing, a figure that has to 4.1 years for women with solid employment increases, which took longer to achieve this and withdrawal-implied and have the first child until much later.
Auβerdem also has the type of work a groβen influence on motherhood, albeit less than the calendar on the empfängnisbereitschaft ", explains the csic-forscherin Margarita Delgado.
The level of education is another factor in the age of the women in the marriage and the first child must be taken into account.
According to the survey, the age at the time of the marriage and the first child the higher, the higher the level of education.
This difference was also in the women of the same age.
For example, the women in the group between 35 and 49 years, depending on whether they are only the main education or a higher education, on average, each with 25.1 or 32.1 for the first time mother.
There is also still, depending on their level of education, another difference between the women.
While the women with Hauptschlussabschluss even before its first permanent employment and their first child, making it the women with a medium or high school completion exactly the other way around and find a permanent employment and marry later and then have their first child, Delgado.
