New programmes for the evaluation of vehicles
In these days of storms and accidents not only deserve the motor workshops
Every day, thousands of vehicles that are involved in an accident in the workshops, where a accountants towed the damage and the cost of the repairs must assess.
Not a single accident is equal and the calculation of the cost of the parts and working hours can be a long and complex task.
The calculation of the repair cost of between 20,000 and 30,000 euros by hand, einschlieβlich of parts and working hours, can take up to two or three hours.
It is, however, with the support of the latest computer tools a matter of minutes
That is why almost 100% of the experts use this type of systems.
The services and application providers for the evaluation of accidents and repair, gathering the information they receive from the manufacturers, to deal with it then and they offer their customers in the form of a useful programme.
In Spain is Audatex, part of the American group Solera, the market leader; 80% of all opinions, with their products.
The other two companies, which compete with the Tool-market for evaluation and draw up a report, GtMotive and Eurotax.
The work with the data which the manufacturers, is anything but simple.
According to Eduardo Velázquez, sales manager of Audatex, has worked with 63 manufacturers and importers, with each one of them is the information in a different format.
Auβerdem will always gröβer handles amount of data, to the point that in the last five years or longer versions, variants and Motorisierungen came on the market than in the entire 15 years before.
As soon as a new car on the market, the work begins for the companies.
It is a difficult task, because jedeseinzelnde of thousands of vehicles parts must be entered katagolisiert, and its price.
In addition, each model of an "intelligent" chart picture drawn to different parts of the vehicle "click".
If it is a much sold model, the work can be completed in a week, if the process is progressing quickly.
If it is a less gebräuchliches car, it can take up to three or four months. Currently has Audatex in 99.2% of the cars in Spain displaced on full information.
Among the more rarefied models they have, for example, information about the Porsche models, but not on Ferrari or were.
In terms of the sailing on the road car park, it is over 99%.
For the implementation of the documentation and the production of databases, Audatex worldwide on eight (Spain, France, Germany, the United States, Brazil, Mexico, China and Japan) distributed centres and each of them has specialised in certain brands.
The national headquarters is located in Alcobendas (Madrid).
There are more than a hundred technicians (usually experts for engineering) simultaneously with three computer screens.
Audatex invested 90 million euros per year in the preparation of these databases.
Every month they take 2.5 million data on and their customers get the updates every second day.
The drafting of this enormous flow of information allows companies to use these in diverse ways and to offer different products.
The most common use is the use of the repairs and repair, but there are, depending on the country also tools for the management of scrap metal parts or for the calculation of the Feil- or residual value of a car.
The only companies that on a leader on the value of used cars in Spain, is Eurotax.
Audatex provides this offer is not in Spain, but in the United States.
In the review of the products, the Audatex, one can easily offers an overview of the kind of support they are industry experts.
This company offers ten different tools, with the star of the products AudaPlus is a standard solution to Begutachutng of accidents for the experts.
It involves vehicles, motorcycles and light and heavy industrial vehicles.
Auβer the cost of the parts, it contains the repair times estimated by the manufacturer or the Lackierungspreise.
This showed up will depending on its intended use, that is, for every opinion, paid.
The most expensive it will be for clients, it is rare for a maximum of ten times a month, namely 5.75 euros per month.
By contrast, every insurance company, carries out the thousands of opinions, the price with Audatex.
With other products, such as AudaVIN can be a vehicle and equipment with which it ran from the assembly band, only by the chassis number fully identify.
AudaGlass deals with the car windows, and AudaSubastas is one for the professional market open service on the Internet, with the one for vehicles that have been declared to the total damage, can offer.
Their statistics service is very useful in the identification of trends, the implementation of geodemographischen analyses or for the purpose of obtaining information about the derogations for brand and model.
You can, for example, to investigate how many models of a certain Automarke because of breakdowns in the workshop had or how many of them in a certain period were involved in a serious accident.
Gt motives is the only Spanish company, which is the development of this type of computer tools.
It sells, among other Gt Estimate, which also is intended for consultants and on the same kind of digital images, access to parts or prices and official working hours of the manufacturer.
